metadata.name: Surreal Visions
metadata.description:
AI Surrealism work contains concepts where inanimate objects turn into good or evil monsters, works convey a non-ordinary and mystical atmosphere.

"Surreal Visions" is exclusively created for the AI Surrealism exhibition at Oculus NYC, hosted by Superchief Gallery NFT and Exquisite Workers. The largest AI art show in history, featuring 100 AI artists, on June 2-8, 2023, is curated by Anna Dart and Roger Haus.
